Parley - defensive trick
------------------------------------------------------------
The swashbuckler can attempt to halt combat in a room by
negotiating a truce.  Success depends on the intelligence
and charisma of the swashbuckler, and the charisma and
wisdom of the people in the room.  The swashbuckler need
not be in combat himself; he can attempt to stop any combat
in the room.

GL:  8
SP: 30
command:  parley
duration: permanent (until attacked again)
